Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Public back Carter on hostage crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h40h
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Dec 1979
Kennedy blasts Shah while public back President Carter's careful handling of the hostage crisis. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less